{"tid":2496048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改制草案文件有錯漏 　中華煤氣變「媒」氣 　建制派憂相關機構選委資格受影響","createTime":"2021-04-19T14:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T14:22:50.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d479f29a4b3baf749e0faa199b087303f05ce8e1","tid":2496048,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XaB-3bt2QSoKsgBjKdBsl_rDrZw=/535x356/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QTOW22QMCRCF5DMFGVIBMIGTEI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXaB-3bt2QSoKsgBjKdBsl_rDrZw%3D%2F535x356%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQTOW22QMCRCF5DMFGVIBMIGTEI.JPG&h=8ef36b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府提交的修改選舉制度綜合條例草案，文件有不少錯漏，政制及內地事務局常秘鄧忍光稱，如發現草案有手民之誤，當局會以修正案方式進行處理。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i32Gv3uaLLoKcurC_RTahUptjuw=/535x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L2EIIUXH4RGWPE6U64U5Y7ALZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi32Gv3uaLLoKcurC_RTahUptjuw%3D%2F535x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL2EIIUXH4RGWPE6U64U5Y7ALZE.jpg&h=efd12a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉劉淑儀問到「中華全國歸國華僑聯合會香港特別行政區委員」與「中華海外聯誼會香港特別行政區理事」有何具體分別，政制局首席助理秘書長只說屬不同的全國性組織。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n立法會下午（19日）續就政府提交的修改選舉制度綜合條例草案舉行第3次會議，委員會已進入逐條審議階段，發問議員寥寥可數，而包括熱血公民鄭松泰在內的議員均發現政府文件有不少錯漏，包括將屬於選委會工程界選民的「香港中華煤氣有限公司」寫成「中華『媒』氣有公司」，以及將「機場管理局」寫成「機『埸』管理局」。<br />\n<br />\n有建制派議員擔心，上述手民之誤會影響相關機構的選委資格；政制及內地事務局常秘鄧忍光回應稱，如發現草案有手民之誤，當局會以修正案方式進行處理。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/2ZIGNWS3WJHCHPWUKM433RIW3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F2ZIGNWS3WJHCHPWUKM433RIW3I%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuG%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=dbddacad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F2ZIGNWS3WJHCHPWUKM433RIW3I%2F&h=df569e02\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/2ZIGNWS3WJHCHPWUKM433RIW3I/</a>"},{"pid":"c770dfb5813001488241f30bac099586e5e9a2da","tid":2496048,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"腦裝屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00b2bc39d9bcefcfa082645d63ebd00d11c3612","tid":2496048,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"支那狗用拼音打字"},{"pid":"a7589979fbe5d808ca8bf630b2f43f2ceb37d1d8","tid":2496048,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"差不多先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10231baefaf0aceda38c3d34a8b0ce370f8ac56","tid":2496048,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"江嘉敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c425c7866d78f765fef4ad42546f8ef52a86cb","tid":2496048,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"好心嗰班忠誠廢物扮反對派都扮得好番啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫你開會審案你就同我喺度玩中文proofreading<br />\n使咪十幾